Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我早有準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 能夠到達這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫
